what_worked: Applied date_cte_isolate, multi_dimension_prefetch, multi_date_range_cte, prefetch_fact_join achieving 5.23x speedup
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering multiple dimension tables in parallel reduces join fan-out; Separate CTEs for each date alias avoids ambiguous multi-way date joins; Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input
